&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;The Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We are seeking an exceptionally talented individual to join our team as a Campus Recruiting Summer Intern. A successful candidate will be a driven, self-starter who is passionate about working with people. As well as&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;taking pride in the delivery of your work, you&amp;nbsp;will be&amp;nbsp;able&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;demonstrate&amp;nbsp;close attention to detail and excellent organizational skills,&amp;nbsp;helping&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;us explore AI-powered ways to streamline our workflow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;You will create strong relationships, be able to communicate effectively,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;and pilot AI projects that improve scheduling, data tracking, and candidate engagement&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;The Campus Recruiting Intern will work alongside our Talent Acquisition Team to develop a big-picture understanding of our campus hiring business, brand&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;values&amp;nbsp;and act as a champion of our tagline “Talent is our Strategy.”&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:120,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:257}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
